006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008/**
009 * A marker interface for an information element that is a field model type.
010 *
011 */
012public interface IField extends INamedModelElement, IAttributable {
013  /**
014   * Provides the Metaschema model type of "FIELD".
015   *
016   * @return the model type
017   */
018  @Override
019  default ModelType getModelType() {
020    return ModelType.FIELD;
021  }
022}
